<br>
Primaryhand:-<br>
((2*Damage)+Damage Bonus)/Delay)*10)*(1+DA))<br>
<br>
Offhand:-<br>
((2*Damage)/Delay)*DW)*10)*(1+DA))<br>
<br>
Where:-<br>
DA= likelihood of Double Attack happening<br>
DW= likelihood of Dual Wield Happening <br>
<br>
By the way, I got a similar equation out of the above formulae as well.  Is anyone able to confirm that these are at all acurate?  <br>
<br>
If so I would be happy to throw together a spiffy spreadsheet, and maybe even link it to another with weps.<br>
